  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink84-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattaiyar maṉaikkaṇ taṅkip puṇarccik kuṟiyōṭu vāyil vēṇṭi vanta
          talaimakaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink84">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>ceviyiṟ kēṭpiṉuñ colliṟantu vekuḷvōḷ</l>
          <l>kaṇṇiṟ kāṇi ṉeṉṉā kuvaḷko</l>
          <l>ṉaṟuvī yaimpāṉ makaḷi rāṭun</l>
          <l>taiit taṇkayam pōlap</l>
          <l>palarpaṭin tuṇṇuniṉ parattai mārpē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Even if she [only] hears [it] with [her] ears, she'll be furious beyond words. </l>
          <l> [But] what will happen to her if, with [her own] eyes, she sees</l>
          <l> your chest [touched by] another woman, </l>
          <l> where many settle and eat – </l>
          <l> as though it were a cool tank </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> in [the month of] Tai</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> where women bathe, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> [their hair plaited into] five strands </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> [and adorned with] fragrant flowers? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
